## Stack Overview

| Component           | Technology                                      |
| ------------------- | ----------------------------------------------- |
| **Type**            | Full-Stack Monorepo (Backend + Frontend)        |
| **Backend Lang**    | Python 3.12                                     |
| **Backend Frame**   | Django 5.x                                      |
| **GraphQL**         | Strawberry GraphQL (strawberry-graphql[django]) |
| **Database**        | PostgreSQL 16                                   |
| **Backend Server**  | Gunicorn / Nginx                                |
| **Frontend Frame**  | Next.js 15 (App Router)                         |
| **Frontend Lang**   | TypeScript 5.x                                  |
| **UI Library**      | React 19                                        |
| **Styling**         | Tailwind CSS v4                                 |
| **GraphQL Client**  | Apollo Client (or urql)                         |
| **Code Generation** | GraphQL Code Generator                          |
| **Node Runtime**    | Node.js 22 (where required)                     |
| **Backend Tests**   | pytest, pytest-django                           |
| **Frontend Tests**  | Vitest, React Testing Library                   |
| **Container**       | Docker Compose                                  |

