## Architecture

This is a **full-stack monorepo** combining:

```
syntek-website/
├── backend/          # Django + Strawberry GraphQL API
└── frontend/         # Next.js (App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind)
```

The Next.js frontend consumes the Django GraphQL API. Both services run via Docker Compose.

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                     frontend/ (Next.js)                          │
│  - React 19 + TypeScript                                         │
│  - Tailwind CSS v4                                               │
│  - Apollo Client → GraphQL queries/mutations                     │
│  - Generated TypeScript types from Strawberry schema             │
└──────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────┘
                           │ GraphQL API (http://localhost:8000/graphql/)
                           ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                     backend/ (Django)                            │
│  - Strawberry GraphQL — Queries, Mutations, Subscriptions        │
│  - JWT Authentication (strawberry-django-jwt or similar)         │
│  - PostgreSQL 16                                                 │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

