## Key Locations

### Backend (`backend/`)

| Path                         | Purpose                                    |
| ---------------------------- | ------------------------------------------ |
| `backend/apps/core/`         | Shared utilities, root GraphQL schema      |
| `backend/apps/core/schema.py`| Root Strawberry schema                     |
| `backend/apps/users/`        | User management and authentication         |
| `backend/apps/users/schema.py` | User GraphQL types, queries, mutations   |
| `backend/config/settings/`   | Environment-specific Django settings       |
| `backend/tests/`             | pytest test suite                          |

### Frontend (`frontend/`)

| Path                              | Purpose                               |
| --------------------------------- | ------------------------------------- |
| `frontend/src/app/`               | Next.js App Router pages              |
| `frontend/src/components/`        | App-specific React components         |
| `frontend/src/graphql/`           | GraphQL queries, mutations, fragments |
| `frontend/src/graphql/generated/` | Auto-generated types and hooks        |
| `frontend/src/hooks/`             | Custom React hooks                    |
| `frontend/src/contexts/`          | React Context providers               |
| `frontend/src/services/`          | Non-GraphQL services                  |
| `frontend/src/utils/`             | Utility functions                     |
| `frontend/src/types/`             | Shared TypeScript types               |

